name: Dr. Christine Lo
about: In 1987, Dr. Christine Lo received her Doctor of Medicine in Dentistry degree from the University of Sheffield in the United Kingdom. She began her dental career working in both London and Hong Kong. Dr. Lo is a Prosthodontist in Boston and received her speciality degree at Boston University in 1992. She continued there as an Assistant Clinical Professor for 10 years in the Department of Postgraduate Prosthodontics. Dr. Lo is proud to share her expertise in prosthodontics with the patients of Smile Design Boston.
